description._content: Description: Halefka Northern Range. Aleppo Pine self-sown seedlings under mature trees; Kartaldagh Forest, Northern Range. Many old trees removed. Location: Halefka, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Description: Halefka Northern Range. Yaila, 3000' elevation with surrounding natural regeneration of Aleppo-Pine. Location: Halefka, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/697 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
